From the Ionic [Lifecycle Events][1], &lt;code&gt;ionViewDidLoad()&lt;/code&gt; runs after the page is loaded, so you are calling your function after the view is loaded.&lt;br&gt;

Instead call your method in &lt;code&gt;ionViewWillEnter()&lt;/code&gt; method.


  [1]: https://ionicframework.com/docs/v3/api/navigation/NavController/#lifecycle-events

